    "title_en": "Differential forms, open-closed maps, and Gromov-Witten axioms",
    "abstract_en": "We construct open-closed maps on various versions of Hochschild and cyclic homology of the Fukaya $A_\\infty$ algebra of a Lagrangian submanifold modeled on differential forms. The $A_\\infty$ algebra may be curved. Properties analogous to Gromov-Witten axioms are verified. The paper is written with applications in mind to gravitational descendants and obstruction theory.",
